        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"307953\">Ruben Van de Velde</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/How.20to.20formalize.20the.20following.20set.20proposition.20in.20lean/near/456770849\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>If you're talking about <code>Set X</code>, it's not true. For types, you might explicitly construct a larger type with Option</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>Option Nat ~= Nat</code> would like to have a say <span aria-label=\"wink\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f609\" role=\"img\" title=\"wink\">:wink:</span></p>",
